central_degraded.description:
The CCU connection for **{instance_name}** is in a degraded state.

Reason: {reason}

Some interfaces are disconnected. The integration is attempting automatic recovery.

paramset_inconsistency.description:
{device_count} device(s) have parameters in the schema that are not present in the actual MASTER paramset. This indicates stale device files in the HmIPServer (crRFD) after a firmware update.

**Affected devices:** {device_addresses}

**Missing parameters ({parameter_count}):** {missing_parameters}

**Resolution:** Perform a factory reset on the affected device(s) via the CCU WebUI. This will force the HmIPServer to refresh its device data.
